#: app/templates/upload.html:16
msgid "Only upload files that were previously hosted on AndroidFileHost"
msgstr "Téléversez uniquement des fichiers provenant d'AndroidFileHost"

#: app/templates/upload.html:17
msgid "Provide as much metadata as possible to help with approval"
